Speaking for myself, I definitely appreciate an assumed lunch time slot, or at least no responsibilities after say 1:00 pm.  This gives us (and our sales team) the flexibility to get to the airport around dinner time and possible get home in time to see the family before bed.&lt;br /&gt;
